前活结乐队鼓手杰伊·温伯格正在制作个人专辑https://www.nme.com/news/music/ex-slipknot-drummer-jay-weinberg-is-working-on-a-solo-album-3825531?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=ex-slipknot-drummer-杰伊·温伯格正在制作个人专辑Surej SinghThu, 02 Jan 2025 04:50:18 +0000 Music NewsNewsMetalRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3825531 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/jay-weinberg@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/jay-weinberg@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/jay-weinberg@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/jay-weinberg@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/jay-weinberg@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/jay-weinberg@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/jay-weinberg@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Weinberg 于 2023 年底离开 Slipknot，此后一直为自杀倾向鼓吹</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ex-slipknot-drummer-jay-weinberg-is-working-on-a-solo-album-3825531">前活结乐队鼓手杰伊·温伯格 (Jay Weinberg) 正在制作一张</a>首张发表在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上的个人专辑。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/jay-weinberg@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/jay-weinberg@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/jay-weinberg@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/jay-weinberg@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/jay-weinberg@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/jay-weinberg@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/jay-weinberg@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/slipknot">活结乐队</a>前鼓手杰伊·温伯格透露，他计划今年录制一张个人专辑。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slipknot-clown-interview-anniversary-tour-new-album-look-outside-your-window-3822347">小丑谈论 Slipknot 25 周年巡演和未来：“我们现在可能有几张专辑”</a></strong></li></ul><p>温伯格于 2014 年加入 Slipknot，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slipknot-announce-departure-of-drummer-jay-weinberg-3531261">于 2023 年 11 月被爱荷华州金属公司解雇</a>。他于 12 月 31 日在社交媒体上分享了他的新年计划。</p><p>虽然温伯格<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/former-slipknot-drummer-jay-weinberg-joins-suicidal-tendencies-3597073">现在是朋克传奇乐队“自杀倾向”的鼓手</a>，但他表示今年他计划“在录音室录制更多音乐”。这似乎将成为他的首个个人项目——他说这个项目已经酝酿多年，而且似乎也会看到他弹吉他。 </p><figure id="attachment_3531467" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3531467" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3531467" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/jay-weinberg@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/jay-weinberg@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/jay-weinberg@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/jay-weinberg@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/jay-weinberg@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/jay-weinberg@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/jay-weinberg@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3531467" class="wp-caption-text">杰·温伯格 (Jay Weinberg) 与活结乐队 (Slipknot) 一起表演。图片来源：Venla Shalin/Redferns</figcaption></figure><p>他在 Instagram 上写道：“我 2025 年的目标之一是在录音室录制更多音乐——从我自己已经写了很长一段时间的材料开始。其中一些是我从 20 岁出头就开始努力的。</p><p>他继续说道：“从那以后我就再也没有碰过这些歌曲，直到最近我才感受到灵感，重新拿起吉他，再次弹奏这些东西。这是一次充实的经历，我告诉你——我开始喜欢这些歌曲的发展方向。最终决定在来年发行一些新音乐，感觉很好。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DENrDX3JG61/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.2